                                            nConI.RedirectSound = Connection.Protocol.RDP.RDPSounds.BringToThisComputer
                                        Case 1
                                            nConI.RedirectSound = Connection.Protocol.RDP.RDPSounds.LeaveAtRemoteComputer
                                        Case 2
